title: Howard Stern (Phony Phone-A-Thon)
description:
Howard Stern (Phony Phone-A-Thon)  (3:55:16)

Join the Stern Show’s master pranksters Sal Governale and Richard Christy as they play some of their favorite phony phone calls and give special behind-the-scenes stories of how some of their classics came about.

Fellow staffers Fred Norris, Gary Dell’Abate, and more will also share some of their personal favorite phony phone call picks.

From Tradio and Swap Shop calls to celebrity impressionists to pranks using clips of Howard, it’s hours of phony phone call fun! Plus, a ton of great song parodies.
